title: Bump nltk from 3.4 to 3.4.5

labels.name: dependencies
labels.description: Pull requests that update a dependency file

body:
Bumps [nltk](https://github.com/nltk/nltk) from 3.4 to 3.4.5.
Changelog *Sourced from [nltk's changelog](https://github.com/nltk/nltk/blob/develop/ChangeLog).* > Version 3.5 2019-08-07 > * drop support for Python 2 > * minor bug fixes and clean ups > > Thanks to the following contributors to 3.5: > Nicolas Darr, Gerhard Kremer, Liling Tan > > Version 3.4.5 2019-08-20 > * Fixed security bug in downloader: Zip slip vulnerability - for the unlikely > situation where a user configures their downloader to use a compromised server > https://cve.mitre.org/cgi-bin/cvename.cgi?name=CVE-2019-14751) > > Thanks to the following contributors to 3.4.5: > Mike Salvatore > > Version 3.4.4 2019-07-04 > * fix bug in plot function (probability.py) > * add improved PanLex Swadesh corpus reader > > Thanks to the following contributors to 3.4.4: > Devashish Lal, Liling Tan > > Version 3.4.3 2019-06-07 > > * add Text.generate() > * add QuadgramAssocMeasures > * add SSP to tokenizers > * return confidence of best tag from AveragedPerceptron > * make plot methods return Axes objects > * don't require list arguments to PositiveNaiveBayesClassifier.train > * fix Tree classes to work with native Python copy library > * fix inconsistency for NomBank > * fix random seeding in LanguageModel.generate > * fix ConditionalFreqDist mutation on tabulate/plot call > * fix broken links in documentation > * fix misc Wordnet issues > * update installation instructions > > Thanks to the following contributors to 3.4.3: > alvations, Bharat123rox, cifkao, drewmiller, free-variation, henchc > irisxzhou, nick-ulle, ppartarr, simonepri, yigitsever, zhaoyanpeng > > Version 3.4.1 2019-04-17 > > * add chomsky_normal_form for CFGs > * add meteor score > * add minimum edit/Levenshtein distance based alignment function > * allow access to collocation list via text.collocation_list() > * support corenlp server options > * drop support for Python 3.4 > ... (truncated)
Commits - [`acca8d5`](https://github.com/nltk/nltk/commit/acca8d573878e173379fe190d7f14f298b12dac9) updates for 3.4.5 - [`083bbf0`](https://github.com/nltk/nltk/commit/083bbf00fcc3b5e944fa5e2708a9a06769af0d5b) updates for 3.4.5 - [`f59d7ed`](https://github.com/nltk/nltk/commit/f59d7ed8df2e0e957f7f247fe218032abdbe9a10) CVE-2019-14751: - [`2554ff4`](https://github.com/nltk/nltk/commit/2554ff48feed878ba7e830ada9825196f3eaa86a) updates for 3.4.4 - [`fbda919`](https://github.com/nltk/nltk/commit/fbda91914fee1968cd18a6c3d3ef21871476daee) drop comment about implementation which is no longer accurate, and which did ... - [`8bcc98a`](https://github.com/nltk/nltk/commit/8bcc98a28d3447ca8eaf3f75ae6fb03165319244) Merge pull request [#2319](https://github-redirect.dependabot.com/nltk/nltk/issues/2319) from BLaZeKiLL/BLaZeKiLL-polt-bug-fix - [`f6a4f38`](https://github.com/nltk/nltk/commit/f6a4f38351b1a195fa220776b89c982ff8f55ba3) Merge pull request [#2291](https://github-redirect.dependabot.com/nltk/nltk/issues/2291) from alvations/better-panlex - [`8c75c56`](https://github.com/nltk/nltk/commit/8c75c567d8bacc2df2b7c375130153a8a428455f) Merge pull request [#2324](https://github-redirect.dependabot.com/nltk/nltk/issues/2324) from minho42/Fix-typo - [`afe23b3`](https://github.com/nltk/nltk/commit/afe23b3f343cd2f7f5e15213be581cf6ee633c36) Fix typo - [`ecdcc57`](https://github.com/nltk/nltk/commit/ecdcc57b56ea9109872cf442f6445f68f0acdbb9) fixed retrieval of conditions from kwargs - Additional commits viewable in [compare view](https://github.com/nltk/nltk/compare/3.4...3.4.5)
